# SECURITY REPORT

## Overview
This report summarizes all security and input validation tests performed for the backend APIs. The system includes the following protections:
- Payload whitelisting
- Schema-level validation (Joi)
- Request throttling (express-rate-limit)
- Header hardening (Helmet + CORS)
- Query sanitization (express-mongo-sanitize)
- XSS prevention (xss-clean)
- Async jobs observability (BullMQ + structured logging)
- Request tracing (X-Request-ID)

---

